---
import MainLayout from "../../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { SITE_TITLE } from "../../consts";
---

<MainLayout title={`About ${SITE_TITLE}`} headerVariant="default">
    <main class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
        <!-- Hero Section -->
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 lg:py-24">
            <section class="mb-20">
                <h1
                    class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4 tracking-tight"
                >
                    About {SITE_TITLE}
                </h1>
                <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-8">
                    Everything you need to know about our platform
                </p>
                <div
                    class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed"
                >
                    <p>
                        Give Back Guide is growing database of travel
                        experiences, tours and accommodation, but with a twist.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        All of the listings on our platform have a positive
                        impact on people, places and the planet. Many are social
                        enterprises or community projects, some are co-ops,
                        others are non-profits or just regular businesses with a
                        commitment to do something good for their local
                        communities or ecosystems.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        As well as regular tourist-orientated things (like
                        tours, hotels, retreats, museums and experiences), we
                        also have cafes, shops and restaurants. Everything you
                        would normally do on a trip, but with added positive
                        impact for the places you love to visit.
                    </p>
                    <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                        Give Back Guide is a non-profit organisation. We are not
                        for sale. We exist for the public good.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>

        <!-- Photo Grid -->
        <section class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 pb-12">
            <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <div>
                    <img
                        class="h-auto max-w-full rounded-lg"
                        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dnxl7wsnx/image/upload/v1744197198/oslo-fjord-clean-up_yydfap.jpg"
                        alt="A group of paddleboarders help to clean up Oslo Fjord"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
                <div>
                    <img
                        class="h-auto max-w-full rounded-lg"
                        src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dnxl7wsnx/image/upload/v1744197237/santorini-animal-welfare_zduqln.jpg"
                        alt="A group of volunteers help to care for animals in Santorini"
                        loading="lazy"
                    />
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Why We Exist Section - Full Width -->
        <section class="bg-black py-20 lg:py-32">
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16">
                <!-- Left Column: Big Statement -->
                <div class="px-8 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 flex items-center">
                    <p
                        class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl font-medium leading-tight tracking-tight text-left"
                    >
                        <span class="text-gray-400">Over-tourism, </span><span
                            class="text-white"
                            >financial leakage,
                        </span><span class="text-gray-400"
                            >community and cultural erosion,
                        </span><span class="text-white"
                            >disproportionately high carbon emissions,
                        </span><span class="text-gray-400"
                            >animal exploitation,
                        </span><span class="text-white"
                            >the list goes on and on…</span
                        >
                    </p>
                </div>

                <!-- Right Column: Explanation -->
                <div
                    class="px-8 lg:px-16 xl:px-24 space-y-6 text-xl text-white leading-relaxed flex flex-col justify-center"
                >
                    <p>
                        The travel industry is currently run, in general, by
                        placing most of the emphasis on what the traveller
                        wants. This leads to a multitude of issues.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        Give Back Guide operates on the belief and assumption
                        that regenerative travel is the answer (or at least part
                        of the answer) to so many of these issues.
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        To travel regeneratively is to leave a place in a better
                        state than you found it. Regenerative travel shifts the
                        focus from the individual traveller to the destination.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- How We Came to Be Section - Full Width -->
        <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 py-20 lg:py-32">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-12 tracking-tight"
                >
                    How Give Back Guide came to be
                </h2>
                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-center">
                    <div
                        class="space-y-6 text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed order-2 md:order-1"
                    >
                        <p>
                            Give Back Guide was founded by Matt & Jade (that's
                            us). Whilst on a six month tour of Southeast Asia,
                            we found ourselves wanting our travels to be more
                            meaningful. We found ourselves gravitating towards
                            social enterprise cafes and shops, community litters
                            picks and animal sanctuaries. We immediately felt
                            the difference. We were meeting awesome local people
                            who were passionate and actively involved in their
                            communities and our travels were having a positive
                            impact on the places we visited. It was a win-win!
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            We were however surprised by how much effort and
                            time it took to find projects to engage with, so we
                            started to collate all the projects we found. We
                            soon realised that our collection might be useful to
                            others, so we released it publicly for free.
                        </p>
                        <p class="font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-white">
                            From that moment, Give Back Guide was born.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="px-4 sm:px-8 order-1 md:order-2">
                        <img
                            src="https://res.cloudinary.com/dnxl7wsnx/image/upload/v1744197180/matt-jade-singapore-cloud-forest_wc25cv.jpg"
                            alt="Matt and Jade at Singapore Cloud Forest"
                            class="w-full max-w-lg mx-auto rounded-lg"
                            loading="lazy"
                        />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <!-- Our Values Section - Full Width -->
        <section class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800 py-20 lg:py-32">
            <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
                <h2
                    class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-16 tracking-tight text-center"
                >
                    Our Values
                </h2>
                <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-8 lg:gap-12">
                    <!-- Transparency & Integrity -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-lg"
                    >
                        <h3
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                        >
                            Transparency & Integrity
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg"
                        >
                            We believe in open communication and we want our
                            users to feel like they can trust us. We can help to
                            bring this about by being open with how we are
                            funded and how we run our business.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Regeneration & Sustainability -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-lg"
                    >
                        <h3
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                        >
                            Regeneration & Sustainability
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg mb-4"
                        >
                            We want tourism to be a tool for regeneration and we
                            exist to provide a means for people to bring this
                            about. In short, we want the world to be left in a
                            better state than we found it.
                        </p>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg"
                        >
                            We aim for our business practices to be genuinely
                            sustainable, the details of which can be found in
                            our <a href="/sustainability/"
                                >Climate Action Plan</a
                            >.
                        </p>.
                    </div>

                    <!-- Equity -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-lg"
                    >
                        <h3
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                        >
                            Equity
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg"
                        >
                            We want society to progress, and we don't want
                            anyone to be left out. We will challenge systems
                            that create imbalance, lift up historically
                            marginalised communities and always ask ourselves
                            whether we can do better.
                        </p>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Community -->
                    <div
                        class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-700 p-8 lg:p-12 rounded-lg"
                    >
                        <h3
                            class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
                        >
                            Community
                        </h3>
                        <p
                            class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed text-lg"
                        >
                            Our work is rooted in the belief that meaningful
                            change happens when people come together. We intend
                            to listen, to learn and to collaborate. We recognise
                            that we are a part of a wider network, and that
                            collective action has greater effect.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
</MainLayout>
